# ratio layout flutter

> mmbuat layout fleksibel 

```dart
 @override
  Widget build(BuildContext context) {
    // TODO: implement build
    return Row(
      children: <Widget>[
        Expanded(
          child: AspectRatio(
            aspectRatio: 12/6,
            child: Container(
              color: Colors.blue,
            ),
          ),
        ),
        Expanded(
          child: AspectRatio(
            aspectRatio: 12/1,
            child: Container(
              color: Colors.yellow,
              child: Text("apa kabarnya"),
            ),
          ),
        )
      ],
    );
    
```
